entries.npc_11: Thank you for the kind words.  I'll remember them if I ever have to arrest you.
entries.player_10: Well, you're doing a great job.
entries.npc_5: It means keeping the streets safe for citizens like yourself.
entries.npc_9: I don't even know who that is.
entries.npc_8: Jabba is a respected businessman, and I shall hear no more of this slander.
entries.player_5: Why don't you do something about the criminals?
entries.npc_3: I'm in charge of security here on Tatooine.
entries.npc_7: Perhaps you should get a job first.
entries.npc_6: I don't have time for fools like you.
entries.player_4: Maybe I should get a title.
entries.player_3: If you're so respected why are you stuck here on Tatooine?
entries.npc_2: It's called a title.  That's what you get when you're respected at your job.
entries.player_2: What is it that you do here?
entries.npc_1: What is it that you want?
